      <strong>Key Takeaways</strong>
      <ul>
        <li>Every customer visit should have a clear purpose.</li>
        <li>Preparation improves every sales conversation.</li>
        <li>Efficient territory planning creates more opportunities.</li>
        <li>Existing customers deserve as much attention as new prospects.</li>
        <li>Organization builds trust and reduces stress.</li>
        <li>Strong relationships generate referrals.</li>
        <li>Continuous learning increases long-term value.</li>
      </ul>
